</example>

*** 将对象序列化

<example>
#1 repr() and eval() function
repr(obj) # change the obj to string
eval(str) # change the string to obj

# for example
>>>s = set()
>>>s.add((1,2))
>>>s.add((1,3))
>>>s.add((1,4))
>>>s.add((2,5))
>>>repr(s)
'set([(1, 2), (1, 5), (2, 3), (2, 4)])'
>>>eval(repr(s))
set([(1, 2), (1, 5), (2, 3), (2, 4)])

# 2 pickle
>>>import pickle
>>>repr(pickle.dumps(s))
>>>pickle.loads(eval(repr(pickle.dumps(s))))

# 3 besides that, json package also can serial the object.
</example>

